{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/april-13-update/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"880 Project Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"17faa46a-ab91-58e9-80b3-344a16eea42f","excerpt":"At the time of writing, I am waiting on my Apple Developer account to proceed beyond pending status. The game now features a minimap. I spent a bit of timeâ€¦","html":"<p><em>At the time of writing, I am waiting on my Apple Developer account to proceed beyond pending status.</em></p>\n<p>The game now features a minimap. I spent a bit of time working through several tutorials before finding one that seemed like a good fit.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/7970d/medical-center-with-minimap.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.60759493670886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Minimap\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/f058b/medical-center-with-minimap.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/c26ae/medical-center-with-minimap.png 158w,\n/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/6bdcf/medical-center-with-minimap.png 315w,\n/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/f058b/medical-center-with-minimap.png 630w,\n/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/40601/medical-center-with-minimap.png 945w,\n/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/78612/medical-center-with-minimap.png 1260w,\n/static/5cfb4a0ed75834e2dfdbf727b2e6d730/7970d/medical-center-with-minimap.png 1908w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Using Unity's official tutorials, I worked through building and (local) publishing the game for iOS. I needed to sign up for an Apple Developer account, then follow a few additional steps. I'm current awaiting the approval of my Apple Developer account.</p>\n<h3>TODO</h3>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> an in-game menu system to click and navigate throughout the game world, rather than using typical controls.</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Apple Developer account configuration</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> load content onto iPad/iPhone</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> add music and sound effects</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> a startup menu</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Latest WebGL Build: <a href=\"https://play.unity.com/mg/other/webgl-6ej\">https://play.unity.com/mg/other/webgl-6ej</a></p>\n<p>Advisor: <a href=\"https://www.towson.edu/fcsm/departments/computerinfosci/facultystaff/ztang.html\">Dr. Ziying Tang</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"April 13","date":"April 13, 2023","description":"The game now includes a working minimap, and pending iOS support."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/project-overview/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Project Overview"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/april-20-update/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"April 20"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"17faa46a-ab91-58e9-80b3-344a16eea42f","previousPostId":"0b418d65-bf57-501e-aed2-a3e5debbcc2a","nextPostId":"273210c7-7dbe-5631-9fe5-37975c1affc9"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}